OL,3,CFamily left 'petrified' after
OL,4,Cfireworks thrown by youths set home on
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FA father says his family has been left
OL,8,F"petrified" after fireworks were
OL,9,Fthrown into their back garden -
OL,10,Fsetting their home on fire.
OL,12,FThe dad, who wants to remain
OL,13,Fanonymous, says he was first alerted
OL,14,Fto the blaze by a neighbour, where he
OL,15,Fwas greeted with flames "as high as
OL,16,Fthe house".
OL,18,FHe attempted to tackle the fire with a
OL,19,Fgarden hose, before emergency services
OL,20,Farrived to help.
