OL,7,F"It's outrageous what an accident can
OL,8,Fcause. I was sat there watching
OL,9,FSaturday night telly with a beer. It
OL,10,Fwas scary, and we shouldn't have to
OL,11,Flive like that."
OL,13,FEmergency services were called
OL,14,Ffollowing reports of the fire and anti-
OL,15,Fsocial behaviour to Whittle Grove in
OL,16,FBolton on 19 October around 8.15pm.
