OL,7,FThrough speaking to his neighbours and
OL,8,Fcollecting doorbell footage, the man
OL,9,Fsaid he was able to piece together
OL,10,Fwhat happened before, during and after
OL,11,Fthe fire.
OL,13,FHe since edited the footage together
OL,14,Fand posted a video on social media in
OL,15,Fa bid to show the dangers of handling
OL,16,Ffireworks unsafely.
OL,18,FIn the video, a group of youths can be
OL,19,Fseen making their way through the
OL,20,Fneighbourhood just off Chorley Old
OL,21,FRoad, before lighting a firework.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
