OL,7,FA bang can then be heard, before the
OL,8,Fvideo cuts to the ferocious fire
OL,9,Fbeginning to spread with the fire
OL,10,Fbrigade arriving.
OL,12,FThe man added: "I'm frustrated now
OL,13,Fbecause my family is petrified. I
OL,14,Fdon't want to do anything to the
OL,15,Fchildren I just want to make them
OL,16,Faware how dangerous it is with
OL,17,FHalloween and bonfire night around the
OL,18,Fcorner.
