OL,3,CFamily left 'petrified' after
OL,4,Cfireworks thrown by youths set home on
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,F"I want to spread a message to other
OL,8,Fteenagers, or adults who mess about
OL,9,Fwith fireworks to be a bit safer."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Greater Manchester
OL,12,FPolice said: "At around 8.15pm on 19
OL,13,FOctober, we responded to reports of
OL,14,Fanti-social behaviour and a fire on
OL,15,FWhittle Grove, Bolton. Thankfully, no-
OL,16,Fone was hurt during the incident.
OL,18,F"If anyone has any information, please
OL,19,Fcontact 101, quoting log 3096 of 19/10/
OL,20,F24."
